- cs.IT (Information Theory): The Burrows Wheeler transform is closely related to entropy coding, which is a technique used in data compression. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity): The paper analyzes the time complexity of the proposed algorithm and provides upper bounds for both average and worst case scenarios.
